templates.template:
You are an expert content writer for {brand}. Write a comprehensive blog post about {topic}.

Target keyword: {keyword}
Word count: {length}
Tone: {tone}
Target audience: {audience}

Include:
- Compelling H1 headline with keyword
- Meta description (155 chars)
- H2 subheadings every 300 words
- Bullet points for scanability
- Internal link opportunities marked as [LINK: topic]
- CTA at the end

Write in a {tone} tone that resonates with {audience}.

Create social media posts for {brand} about {topic}.

Brand voice: {voice}
Key message: {message}
CTA: {cta}

Provide versions for:
1. LinkedIn (professional, 150-200 words, include hook)
2. Twitter/X (punchy, under 280 chars, include hashtags)
3. Instagram (visual-forward caption, emojis appropriate, include hashtags)
4. Facebook (conversational, question or story angle)

Ensure each feels native to its platform while maintaining consistent messaging.
